  m_text: "Camera: \r\nW A S D = Move camera\r\nMouse Wheel = Zoom\r\nRight Click
    Hold = Orbit camera around the clicked point\r\nReset Camera Button = Return
    to the default view\n\nPlacement\r\nLeft Click = Paint or place\r\nHold Left
    Click in Obstacle or Unit mode = Prepare placement rotation\r\nArrow Keys while
    holding = Rotate the object before placing\r\nRelease Left Click = Confirm placement\nMiddle
    Click: Erase\n\nSave / Load\r\nType a level name in the file name field\r\nSave
    will create or overwrite a JSON in:\r\nAssets/Resources/LevelLayouts"
